es-img.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fnotes-img.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fnotes-img.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fnotes-img.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fnotes-img.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div></div><a href=\"/notes-img.png\" download=\"ACT-notes.png\" class=\"inline-block mt-2 w-11/12 md:w-2/3 text-center px-4 py-2 border border-[#1E4A76] text-[#1E4A76] rounded-md bg-white hover:bg-[#1E4A76] hover:text-white transition text-sm font-medium shadow-sm hover:shadow-md\" aria-label=\"Download ACT notes image\">Download Notes</a><p class=\"text-xs text-[#718096] mt-2 max-w-xs\">High-resolution notes — click Download to save the PDF/image.</p></div></div></div></div></section></div> <aside class=\"lg:col-span-1 space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md border border-[#E2E8F0] p-5\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-[#1E4A76] flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-layout-dashboard w-5 h-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"7\" height=\"9\" x=\"3\" y=\"3\" rx=\"1\"></rect><rect width=\"7\" height=\"5\" x=\"14\" y=\"3\" rx=\"1\"></rect><rect width=\"7\" height=\"9\" x=\"14\" y=\"12\" rx=\"1\"></rect><rect width=\"7\" height=\"5\" x=\"3\" y=\"16\" rx=\"1\"></rect></svg>Your Dashboard</h2><p class=\"text-xs text-[#718096] mt-1\">Track your progress and stay on target</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md border border-[#E2E8F0] p-5\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-[#2D3748]\">Overall Progress</h3><span class=\"text-xs bg-green-100 text-green-700 px-1.5 py-1 rounded-full\">On track</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"relative w-12 h-12\"><svg class=\"w-12 h-12 transform -rotate-90\"><circle cx=\"24\" cy=\"24\" r=\"20\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"4\" fill=\"none\"></circle><circle cx=\"24\" cy=\"24\" r=\"20\" stroke=\"#1E4A76\" stroke-width=\"4\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"125.7\" stroke-dashoffset=\"26.396999999999995\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></circle></svg><div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-[#1E4A76]\">79<!-- -->%</span></div></div><div><p class=\"text-sm text-[#4A5568]\"><span class=\"font-medium\">982</span> / <!-- -->1240<!-- --> correct</p><p class=\"text-sm text-[#4A5568] mt-1\">🔥 <!-- -->12<!-- --> day streak</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md border border-[#E2E8F0] p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-[#2D3748] mb-3\">Score Predictor</h3><div class=\"flex items-end justify-between\"><div><p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-[#1E4A76]\">29</p><p class=\"text-xs text-[#718096]\">predicted composite</p></div><div class=\"text-right\"><p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-[#2D3748]\">Target: <!-- -->32</p><p class=\"text-xs text-[#718096]\">3 points to go</p></div></div><div class=\"w-full bg-[#EDF2F7] h-2 rounded-full mt-3\"><div class=\"bg-[#1E4A76] h-2 rounded-full\" style=\"width:80.55555555555556%\"></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md border border-[#E2E8F0] p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-[#2D3748] mb-3\">Focus Areas</h3><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-sm\"><span class=\"text-[#4A5568]\">Punctuation</span><span class=\"text-xs bg-red-100 text-red-600 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full\">needs work</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-sm\"><span class=\"text-[#4A5568]\">Algebra</span><span class=\"text-xs bg-red-100 text-red-600 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full\">needs work</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-sm\"><span class=\"text-[#4A5568]\">Data Interpretation</span><span class=\"text-xs bg-red-100 text-red-600 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full\">needs work</span></li></ul><a class=\"block text-center mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-[#1E4A76] border border-[#1E4A76] rounded-lg py-2 hover:bg-[#1E4A76] hover:text-white transition\" href=\"/act/Practice-Questions\">Practice Weak Topics</a></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md border border-[#E2E8F0] p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-[#2D3748] mb-2\">Upcoming Mock</h3><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar w-5 h-5 text-[#1E4A76]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[#4A5568]\">Full Test #4 - This Saturday</span></div><button class=\"w-full mt-4 bg-[#1E4A76] text-white text-sm font-medium py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-[#163A5E] transition\">View Details</button></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md border border-[#E2E8F0] p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-[#2D3748] mb-3\">Recent Activity</h3><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"border-b border-[#E2E8F0] pb-2 last:border-0 last:pb-0\"><p class=\"text-xs text-[#718096]\">Today</p><p class=\"text-sm text-[#2D3748] font-medium\">Math Practice - 30 questions</p><p class=\"text-xs text-green-600\">Score: <!-- -->85%</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-[#E2E8F0] pb-2 last:border-0 last:pb-0\"><p class=\"text-xs text-[#718096]\">Yesterday</p><p class=\"text-sm text-[#2D3748] font-medium\">Reading Passage - Social Science</p><p class=\"text-xs text-green-600\">Score: <!-- -->78%</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-[#E2E8F0] pb-2 last:border-0 last:pb-0\"><p class=\"text-xs text-[#718096]\">2 days ago</p><p class=\"text-sm text-[#2D3748] font-medium\">English - Rhetorical Skills</p><p class=\"text-xs text-green-600\">Score: <!-- -->92%</p></div></div><a class=\"block text-center mt-4 text-sm text-[#1E4A76] hover:underline\" href=\"/act/analytics\">View full analytics →</a></div><div class=\"bg-[#EBF5FF] rounded-xl p-4 border border-[#B8D1E6]\"><div class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb w-5 h-5 text-[#1E4A76] flex-shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg><p class=\"text-xs text-[#2D3748]\"><span class=\"font-semibold\">Pro tip:</span> Review your incorrect answers daily to reinforce weak areas. Consistency beats cramming!</p></div></div></aside></div> <div class=\"w-full flex justify-center my-5\"><div class=\"w-full max-w-5xl h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#E2E8F0] to-transparent\"></div></div><section id=\"understanding-act\" class=\"w-full bg-gradient-to-b from-[#F7F9FC] via-white to-white mt-10 py-10 md:px-10 px-0\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"flex flex-col-reverse md:flex-row items-center gap-8\"><div class=\"w-full md:w-2/3 text-center md:text-left\"><h1 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold font-sans leading-tight tracking-tight text-[#1E4A76] md:px-0 px-3\">Understanding the ACT Exam</h1><p class=\"mt-3 text-[#4A5568] font-times text-[17px] md:text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto md:mx-0 md:px-0 px-3\">ACT Overview — Format, sections, scoring, and essential strategies to guide your preparation and test-day performance.</p><div class=\"mt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:gap-4 justify-center md:justify-start md:px-0 px-3\"><a href=\"act/Practice-Questions\" class=\"inline-block px-5 py-3 rounded-lg bg-[#3e6286] text-white text-sm font-semibold shadow hover:bg-[#163A5E] transition hover:shadow-lg\" aria-label=\"Get started with ACT preparation\">Start Preparing</a><button class=\"inline-block mt-3 sm:mt-0 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-[#E2E8F0] text-sm text-[#2D3748] font-medium hover:bg-[#F7F9FC] transition bg-white shadow-sm hover:shadow-md\">See detailed breakdown</button></div></div><div class=\"w-full md:w-1/3 flex justify-center md:justify-end\"><div class=\"w-56 bg-white border border-[#E2E8F0] rounded-2xl p-4 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center h-28\"><div class=\"w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-[#EBF5FF] flex items-center justify-center text-[#1E4A76] text-4xl font-bold\">ACT</div></div><div class=\"mt-3 text-center\"><p class=\"text-sm text-[#718096]\">Timed, multiple-choice sections + optional essay</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"my-8\"></div><div id=\"details\" class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><article class=\"bg-white border border-[#E2E8F0] rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition transform hover:-translate-y-1 \"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-full bg-[#F0F4F8]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-award w-6 h-6 text-[#4A5568]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m15.477 12.89 1.515 8.526a.5.5 0 0 1-.81.47l-3.58-2.687a1 1 0 0 0-1.197 0l-3.586 2.686a.5.5 0 0 1-.81-.469l1.514-8.526\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"6\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-[#2D3748]\">Scoring</h3></div><p class=\"text-[#4A5568] text-sm\">Sections scored 1–36. Composite = average of English, Math, Reading, Science. Writing (essay) scored 2–12 separately. Many colleges accept superscores.</p></article><article class=\"bg-white border border-[#E2E8F0] rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition transform hover:-translate-y-1 \"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-full bg-[#F0F4F8]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock w-6 h-6 text-[#4A5568]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-[#2D3748]\">Timing</h3></div><p class=\"text-[#4A5568] text-sm\">Total time usually ~2h20–2h55 depending on sections. With Writing, expect ~3h40. Practice with section timers to build pacing.</p></article><article class=\"bg-white border border-[#E2E8F0] rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition transform hover:-translate-y-1 \"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-full bg-[#F0F4F8]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-question-mark w-6 h-6 text-[#4A5568]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-[#2D3748]\">Question Types</h3></div><p class=\"text-[#4A5568] text-sm\">Mostly multiple-choice (4 options). Writing requires an analytical essay comparing perspectives — practice planning and timing.</p></article><article class=\"bg-white border border-[#E2E8F0] rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition transform hover:-translate-y-1 hidden sm:block\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-full bg-[#F0F4F8]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open w-6 h-6 text-[#4A5568]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-[#2D3748]\">Resources</h3></div><p class=\"text-[#4A5568] text-sm\">Combine official ACT materials with targeted practice (reading speed drills, timed math sets, and science reasoning passages).</p></article><article class=\"bg-white border border-[#E2E8F0] rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition transform hover:-translate-y-1 hidden sm:block\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-full bg-[#F0F4F8]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-brain w-6 h-6 text-[#4A5568]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 18V5\"></path><path d=\"M15 13a4.17 4.17 0 0 1-3-4 4.17 4.17 0 0 1-3 4\"></path><path d=\"M17.598 6.5A3 3 0 1 0 12 5a3 3 0 1 0-5.598 1.5\"></path><path d=\"M17.997 5.125a4 4 0 0 1 2.526 5.77\"></path><path d=\"M18 18a4 4 0 0 0 2-7.464\"></path><path d=\"M19.967 17.483A4 4 0 1 1 12 18a4 4 0 1 1-7.967-.517\"></path><path d=\"M6 18a4 4 0 0 1-2-7.464\"></path><path d=\"M6.003 5.125a4 4 0 0 0-2.526 5.77\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-[#2D3748]\">Strategy</h3></div><p class=\"text-[#4A5568] text-sm\">Work high-confidence items first, skip &amp; mark for review, and watch pacing. No penalty for guessing — answer every question.</p></article><article class=\"bg-white border border-[#E2E8F0] rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition transform hover:-translate-y-1 hidden sm:block\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-full bg-[#F0F4F8]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-pen-tool w-6 h-6 text-[#4A5568]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15.707 21.293a1 1 0 0 1-1.414 0l-1.586-1.586a1 1 0 0 1 0-1.414l5.586-5.586a1 1 0 0 1 1.414 0l1.586 1.586a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.414z\"></path><path d=\"m18 13-1.375-6.874a1 1 0 0 0-.746-.776L3.235 2.028a1 1 0 0 0-1.207 1.207L5.35 15.879a1 1 0 0 0 .776.746L13 18\"></path><path d=\"m2.3 2.3 7.286 7.286\"></path><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-[#2D3748]\">Practice</h3></div><p class=\"text-[#4A5568] text-sm\">Use official practice tests, simulate test-day conditions, and review mistakes thoroughly to improve accuracy and speed.</p></article></div><div class=\"flex justify-center mt-6 sm:hidden\"><button class=\"px-5 py-2 rounded-lg bg-[#EDF2F7] text-[#2D3748] text-sm font-medium hover:bg-[#E2E8F0] transition\">Show more</button></div></div></section><section id=\"test-structure\" class=\"w-full bg-white py-8 md:px-6 px-0\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto md:px-4 px-2\"><div class=\"w-full py-4 text-center\"><h1 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold font-sans text-[#1E4A76]\">Test Structure</h1><h2 class=\"text-[#4A5568] font-times text-[17px] max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-2\">Test Structure: ACT exam format, section breakdown, and timing information to help you prepare effectively.</h2></div><div class=\"mt-6\"><div class=\"hidden md:block overflow-hidden rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-[#E2E8F0] bg-white font-sans\"><table class=\"min-w-full text-sm\"><thead><tr class=\"bg-[#1E4A76] text-white\"><th class=\"px-6 py-3 text-left font-semibold tracking-wide\">Section</th><th class=\"px-6 py-3 text-left font-semibold tracking-wide whitespace-nowrap\">Time</th><th class=\"px-6 py-3 text-left font-semibold tracking-wide\">Questions</th><th class=\"px-6 py-3 text-left font-semibold tracking-wide\">Format</th></tr></thead><tbody class=\"divide-y divide-[#E2E8F0] bg-white\"><tr class=\"group hover:bg-[#F8FAFC] transition-colors duration-150 \"><td class=\"px-6 py-3 font-medium text-[#111827]\">English</td><td class=\"px-6 py-3 text-[#1E4A76] font-semibold whitespace-nowrap text-sm\">35 minutes</td><td class=\"px-6 py-3 text-[#111827] font-medium whitespace-nowrap text-sm\">50 (40 scored)</td><td class=\"px-6 py-3 text-[#4B5563] max-w-sm text-sm\">Multiple-choice, passage-based</td></tr><tr class=\"group hover:bg-[#F8FAFC] transition-colors duration-150 \"><td class=\"px-6 py-3 font-medium text-[#111827]\">Mathematics</td><td class=\"px-6 py-3 text-[#1E4A76] font-semibold whitespace-nowrap text-sm\">50 minutes</td><td class=\"px-6 py-3 text-[#111827] font-medium whitespace-nowrap text-sm\">45 (41 scored)</td><td class=\"px-6 py-3 text-[#4B5563] max-w-sm text-sm\">Multiple-choice, calculator allowed</td></tr><tr class=\"group hover:bg-[#F8FAFC] transition-colors duration-150 \"><td class=\"px-6 py-3 font-medium text-[#111827]\">Reading</td><td class=\"px-6 py-3 text-[#1E4A76] font-semibold whitespace-nowrap text-sm\">40 minutes</td><td class=\"px-6 py-3 text-[#111827] font-medium whitespace-nowrap text-sm\">36 (27 scored)</td><td class=\"px-6 py-3 text-[#4B5563] max-w-sm text-sm\">Multiple-choice, passage-based</td></tr><tr class=\"group hover:bg-[#F8FAFC] transition-colors duration-150 bg-[#F9FAFB]\"><td class=\"px-6 py-3 font-medium text-[#111827]\">Science<span class=\"ml-2 inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-amber-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-amber-800\">Optional</span></td><td class=\"px-6 py-3 text-[#1E4A76] font-semibold whitespace-nowrap text-sm\">40 minutes</td><td class=\"px-6 py-3 text-[#111827] font-medium whitespace-nowrap text-sm\">40 (34 scored)</td><td class=\"px-6 py-3 text-[#4B5563] max-w-sm text-sm\">Data representation, research summaries, conflicting viewpoints</td></tr><tr class=\"group hover:bg-[#F8FAFC] transition-colors duration-150 bg-[#F9FAFB]\"><td class=\"px-6 py-3 font-medium text-[#111827]\">Writing<span class=\"ml-2 inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-amber-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-amber-800\">Optional</span></td><td class=\"px-6 py-3 text-[#1E4A76] font-semibold whitespace-nowrap text-sm\">40 minutes</td><td class=\"px-6 py-3 text-[#111827] font-medium whitespace-nowrap text-sm\">1 essay</td><td class=\"px-6 py-3 text-[#4B5563] max-w-sm text-sm\">Essay analyzing a complex issue &amp; perspectives</td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"md:hidden space-y-4\"><article class=\"border border-[#E2E8F0] rounded-xl p-5 bg-white shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 border-l-4 border-l-[#1E4A76]\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between\"><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-[#111827]\">English</h3></div><p class=\"text-sm text-[#4B5563] mt-1\">Multiple-choice, passage-based</p></div><div class=\"text-right ml-4\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-[#1E4A76] whitespace-nowrap\">35 minutes</p><p class=\"text-xs font-medium text-[#111827] mt-1 whitespace-nowrap\">50 (40 scored)</p></div></div></article><article class=\"border border-[#E2E8F0] rounded-xl p-5 bg-white shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 border-l-4 border-l-[#1E4A76]\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between\"><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-[#111827]\">Mathematics</h3></div><p class=\"text-sm text-[#4B5563] mt-1\">Multiple-choice, calculator allowed</p></div><div class=\"text-right ml-4\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-[#1E4A76] whitespace-nowrap\">50 minutes</p><p class=\"text-xs font-medium text-[#111827] mt-1 whitespace-nowrap\">45 (41 scored)</p></div></div></article><article class=\"border border-[#E2E8F0] rounded-xl p-5 bg-white shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 border-l-4 border-l-[#1E4A76]\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between\"><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-[#111827]\">Reading</h3></div><p class=\"text-sm text-[#4B5563] mt-1\">Multiple-choice, passage-based</p></div><div class=\"text-right ml-4\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-[#1E4A76] whitespace-nowrap\">40 minutes</p><p class=\"text-xs font-medium text-[#111827] mt-1 whitespace-nowrap\">36 (27 scored)</p></div></div></article><article class=\"border border-[#E2E8F0] rounded-xl p-5 bg-white shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 border-l-4 border-l-amber-400\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between\"><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-[#111827]\">Science</h3><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-amber-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-amber-800\">Optional</span></div><p class=\"text-sm text-[#4B5563] mt-1\">Data representation, research summaries, conflicting viewpoints</p></div><div class=\"text-right ml-4\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-[#1E4A76] whitespace-nowrap\">40 minutes</p><p class=\"text-xs font-medium text-[#111827] mt-1 whitespace-nowrap\">40 (34 scored)</p></div></div></article><article class=\"border border-[#E2E8F0] rounded-xl p-5 bg-white shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 border-l-4 border-l-amber-400\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between\"><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-[#111827]\">Writing</h3><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-amber-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-amber-800\">Optional</span></div><p class=\"text-sm text-[#4B5563] mt-1\">Essay analyzing a compl